survey_response.review_text:
I , a retired Bank Manager ,  shifted to this wonderful city from Chennai recently...  One day, as I developed a severe pain in two front teeth, I google-searched for dentists and zeroed in on Dr Priya Bansal.
  I was advised by the dentist to undergo RCT of two frontline teeth.  The diagnosis, the professional expertise the attitude and the treatment were all good.  Earlier, I used to remark jocularly that between stepping into a dentist's clinic for treatment and entering a gas chamber, i would prefer the latter. Because in the former case there will be a persisting pain and  repeated visits whereas the latter requires one visit only. Perhaps not any more.....with Dr Priya's painless and efficient treatment I am  satisfied  and am able to smile sans inhibition after a mis-aligned tooth was set right with a suitable cap after RCT . In fact the caps are as aesthetically designed with similar contours as the original teeth and I am sure they will long last .  * ** ********* **** **  ****** ****** **********  *** ** **** *** ********* ****** * **** *** *** *** ******...
R Raghothaman,

Dr Priya is an excellent doctor and so is Dr Sudhakar Reddy Surgeon at Priya Dental clinic.

I visited the clinic for my Mother for tooth extraction and implant, though one of 4 tooth extracted was infected very badly which made us nervous, but Dr Priya and Dr Reddy explained everything clearly and it made us confident for the procedure.

What made our experience excellent was due to the fact that my mother was in town only for a week and Drs said 4-5 days is all required and it be all fine which is exactly it happened. 

Over all very satisfied with Drs.

review_reply.reply_text: Dear Usha. Thank you for taking the time to review us. We at Priya dental clinic value all feedback and use it to improve our services. Have an amazing day!

survey_response.review_text: We were new to Bangalore and were looking for a reliable and value for money dentist.  One of our friend / neighbor recommended Priya bansal from Priya dental clinic and we are very happy we choose to go here for the dental treatment. The doctors Priya and team are very friendly and explained the issues in detail and then started with the dental treatment. I Had fillings done for few teeth and also a root canal for one tooth. The fillings and Root canal treatment went on very well. Also got fillings done for my sons teeth.  Thank you so much Priya and team for the wonderful experience at the clinic! We are very happy and satisfied with the treatment. I would surly recommend this place to all my friends and relatives.

Dr. Priya is a absolute genius and a naturally gifted dental artisan with unique and priceless achievements, this is not for any, but few, Dr Priya is a rough diamond forever and ever after. The approach is so natural and friendly with the courage and patience to work a way out to ease the dental complications of a patient is amazing with all the staff and the dental associates have got what it takes to address the health issues with ease. The dental clinic is up to high standards and have a very likeable atmosphere with utmost humility. I have a huge personal experience about dentistry from the UK and EU standards, and can vouch for Priya Dental Clinic matching the same UK and EU standards. Sincerely,

I randomly chanced upon Dr. Priya profile on Practo when I was looking for a doctor close to my place, after suffering from long-term toothache. She turned out to be extremely friendly. I liked the professionalism of the staff and the other doctors who treated me on my multiple sessions. I had a complicated root canal treatment for an upper molar and a deep filling for a decayed lower molar. The doctors did not rush through the treatment, as that could have aggravated the issue. In fact, I had minor issues with the alignment of the crown after the root canal, but the doctor went ahead and fixed that too. I would definitely recommend Dr. Priya, not just for her professionalism but also for the modern methods used in her clinic.

Dr.Priya Mam and the team ensured my wisdom tooth extraction will not be a nightmare to me. Hats off to the team for their utmost dedication and sincerity.My tooth x-ray seemed to be very complicated and i remember calling the mam at night 9:30 post my tooth extraction as the initial days post wisdom tooth extraction will be a sure shot adventure one, mam listened to my problems very keenly and helped me to relieve the pain. Thank you for being such a dedicated doctor. I wish all the best for mam and her team for all the future endeavors.

I had never been to a dentist in my life and Very happy that I chose to go to Dr Priyas clinic. 
I had a chipped upper molar, which although not paining was very uncomfortable and needed treatment. Subsequent checks showed that the opposite molar also needed intervention. I dreaded my 1st visit as I had only heard of visits to the dentist being rated very high on the painful things in life list. But happy to say that Dr. Priya has changed my perception about dental visits completely. 
Doctors and the support team at this clinic are highly competent, professional ,very warm and caring. Clear and patient explanation about the condition of teeth, corrective procedures, alternatives, costs comparison etc are done and without trying to push one into any particular treatment. Very Well appointed clinic with the latest equipment I am very happy with the treatment received which is ongoing. Dr Priya even though well qualified competent and highly trained  is still  a down to earth and a very warm and cheerful and caring person. She has selected a team which complements her both professionally and personally. Very warm and peaceful atmosphere makes one forget that it is a dental clinic and one is here for treatment  I recommend Dr. Priya Bansal and her team  wholeheartedly for all your dental treatments.

Dr. Priya is a fantastic doctor. Puts you at total ease…. Most people are terrified when they have a dental problem and mine was massive! Thanks Dr. Priya for your immense patience,  gentleness and flair with which you handled my case. Indeed very grateful and happy with treatment 🙏🙏🙏🤗🤗🤗🤗🤗🌷🌷🌷🌷🤗🤗

It was painless and precise as the motto of the clinic itself. Dr Priya was extremely patient, thorough and candid. She is quite up to date with the clinical advances and helped tailor make a treatment plan that suited me. I had 3 troublesome and deep cavities with lot of sensitivity plus tooth stains. She dealt with them painlessly. I am extremely happy with the results. My teeth look fantastic and I currently have no sensitivity no matter what I eat. Her oral care advice has proved quite practical and easy to follow.
I would recommend her to anyone looking for a reliable, long term dentist for themselves and their families.

She treats old patients like her own family and tries to put them at ease before the treatment. She knows her job and does it to the T. I .very happy that I found a dentist like her to treat my father, who is 83 years old. I don't even have to accompany my father when he has an appointment. Once he is there, I am sure he will be taken care of nicely.
